{"parentUuid":"dcb0c96a-ffe5-4b9b-8b43-7bcf6284e50b","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"/Users/yizhangpeng/Documents/git-repo/Raytracer","sessionId":"5fe7f844-2aad-4516-a5e1-cd169e1a0cc7","version":"2.1.71","gitBranch":"4.1","slug":"jazzy-yawning-wolf","message":{"id":"msg_1773914559005_xqa59spr0o","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"claude-4.6-opus","content":[{"type":"text","text":"效果很好！光源现在有了明显的真实感：\n\n1. ✅ **光晕效果** — 天花板上光源周围有柔和的白色光晕，从光源向外渐变扩散\n2. ✅ **光线集中效果** — 光源正下方区域更亮，蓝色方块顶面和地板都有受光增强\n3. ✅ **暖色调** — 光源和光晕带有微微暖白色，更像真实灯光\n4. ✅ **性能** — ~35ms/帧，28fps，在 24fps 目标内\n\n性能几乎没有损失（增加的只是几个 `exp()` 和 `dot()` 运算，无额外光线追踪）。渲染效果对比之前有明显提升——光源不再是一个孤立的白色矩形，而是有了真实灯光向周围散射的感觉。"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":133221,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":275,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"type":"assistant","uuid":"e443c101-dc7f-4b04-967c-8fc297885a22","timestamp":"2026-03-19T10:03:01.164Z"}
